@host = http://localhost:5252

# Set @tenantId to filter dead letters to a specific tenant.
@tenantId = <paste-tenant-id-here>

### Get all dead-lettered messages (all tenants)
GET {{host}}/api/dead-letters

###

### Get dead-lettered messages for a specific tenant
GET {{host}}/api/dead-letters/tenant/{{tenantId}}
